{"tid":2510661,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"舉報DSE 影Barcode 戇鳩仔集中區","createTime":"2021-04-30T10:04:44.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-01T06:56:53.000Z","uid":374134,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"631a921e25cf9ef00488515efa2302952b9422b8","tid":2510661,"uid":374134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T10:04:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZM1JYpZER9PRJgYrAMFD12zcJzamXgF9m4z5BxhGQLPS?filename=iFaGxet.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiFaGxet.jpg&h=fda93821&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmTJi8VA1aoGrreBAYTiJpdW4XZcQhQaC3xcSgSwsnAGbz?filename=YQpTomd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYQpTomd.jpg&h=3db3d6ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPgkchVCgaex3PMq5RmaF5DjHdC1v8RWzTxUzvoft4yfk?filename=dfQOWGh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdfQOWGh.jpg&h=6e8202d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n舉報sample  <strong><span class=\"large\">（如果冇資料唔使填）</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\ndse@hkeaa.edu.hk<br />\n<br />\n<p class=\"center\">舉報一名考生 於考場拍照，並在公開個人資料</p><br />\n<br />\n你好<br />\n本人於網上發現有考生（<span class=\"red\"><strong>以社交平台Instagram ____帳戶名義， </strong></span>）於考場拍照，並<span class=\"red\"><strong>（在該平台）</strong></span>公開個人考核資料，嚴重違反考試規例，當中包括：<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">A）考生編號 （___）<br />\nB）Barcode號碼（___）<br />\nC）考核科目：（___<br />\nD）試場資料：（__）<br />\nE）座位號碼：（__）</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n根據考試規例，考生在筆試和口試的紀律「考生不得於考試開始前/期間/完畢後於考室（包括口試的報到室和備試室）內攝影/錄影/錄音，否則會被扣分。考生如將有關相片/錄像錄音以電子公開形式展示，其科目成績會被降級。」<br />\n<br />\n「同時，考試完結時監考員會分開收集答卷及電腦條碼紙。考生不可將電腦條碼貼紙拍攝存檔或將剩餘的電腦條碼貼紙帶離試場，否則會被扣分。考生如以電子或公開形式展示電腦條碼貼紙，其科目成續會被降級。<br />\n<br />\n考生如拍攝電腦條碼貼紙或將其帶離試場並以電子或公開形式展示，其科目成績會被降級。」<br />\n是次事件已嚴重反映考生___有嚴重違反考評局相關條例。<br />\n<br />\n請局方嚴正跟進事件，並回覆本人相關後續的處理事項。謝謝，現附上相關圖片以供跟進。<br />\n<br />\n祝 時祺</blockquote></blockquote></blockquote></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"orange\">睇吓仲有冇更加多戇鳩仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"ebc4dfcdf32380c05c2017c5827a92bc3a8e9925","tid":2510661,"uid":374134,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T10:10:24.000Z","msg":"推到佢哋U"},{"pid":"90c14473e7635ac2234c87434cc094bab2c80ec6","tid":2510661,"uid":397139,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T10:10:33.000Z","msg":"DSE考生殺手<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb0b4992df43dff1eae87048c1a425a7cedde2f4","tid":2510661,"uid":374134,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T10:16:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmWWdzEpMGFaqRP1DSbJ4cAVBBL9GuxfDvy3uWvo1BK9M1?filename=wXCUSmw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwXCUSmw.png&h=e3869608&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n考評局回覆話處理緊<br />\n<br />\n等U啦戇鳩仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98a7600a177417bff0eacfe2999a9f8c3ebcade6","tid":2510661,"uid":291750,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T10:26:08.000Z","msg":"點解要咁做"},{"pid":"c0eb5e52b376eb626d115b7c3615ac91e167b249","tid":2510661,"uid":374134,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"98a7600a177417bff0eacfe2999a9f8c3ebcade6","tid":2510661,"uid":291750,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T10:26:08.000Z","msg":"點解要咁做"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T10:47:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1f292e8455aaa7561e3ec6ec6fc7ec0e2fd5d61","tid":2510661,"uid":374